snippet.title: Piko Interactive Collection 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly off the original Evercade handheld. This cart is noteworthy for being the first to bring in 32-Bit games to the Evercade.

Games:
00:08 - Beast Ball (MegaDrive / Genesis)
02:29 - Eliminator Boat Duel (NES)
05:46 - Football Madness (PlayStation)
08:53 - Full Throttle: All-American Racing (SNES)
11:44 - Hoops: Shut Up and Jam (Mega Drive / Genesis) [Also known as Barkley's Shut Up and Jam]
14:37 - Hoops: Shut Up and Jam 2 (Mega Drive / Genesis) [Also known as Barkley's Shut Up and Jam 2]
17:06 - Power Football (Mega Drive / Genesis)
19:30 - Racing Fever (Game Boy Advance)
23:10 - Soccer Kid (SNES)
27:54 - Summer Challenge (Mega Drive / Genesis)
32:19 - Top Racer 2 (SNES) [Also known as Top Gear 2, which is not to be confused with the BBC show with the same name]
34:58 - Winter Challenge (Mega Drive / Genesis)
37:59 - World Trophy Soccer (Mega Drive / Genesis)
